snippet.title: wHispEring hiLLs Episode 4 - Out now! - the place Silent Hill wasnt ready for.
snippet.description:
Discover the chilling world of Wispering Hills in Episode 4, available now on PC and Xbox! Immerse yourself in a Silent Hill-inspired town and embark on a mind-bending quest as you journey into the depths of the abyss.

🔦 Voiceover by Ryan Negrón: https://www.ryannegron.com/
🎵 Background Music by Myuu (Stillstand): https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCiSKnkKCKAQVxMUWpZQobuQ

If you enjoy our content, support our growth on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/vividian

Join our community on Discord to chat with us and report any bugs:
👾 Discord: https://discord.gg/ywwFVYertz

Learn more about us and the Whispering Hills universe at our official website:
🌐 Website: www.whisperinghills.net

Don't miss out on this eerie adventure – dive into Episode 4 today! 💀🎮
https://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/46871
https://www.moddb.com/mods/whispering-hills-a-silent-hill-overhaul-for-fallout-4
